Cody?

15:19.754 --> 15:23.357
Your dad is here.

15:23.390 --> 15:25.192
It's your dad.

15:25.225 --> 15:28.663
And look,
he's got a grocery bag.

15:28.696 --> 15:30.297
Hey, Pal.

15:30.330 --> 15:35.235
How you doing?

