He sure does love playing
with those noodles.

16:31.492 --> 16:32.760
- Too rough!
- No, it's okay.

16:32.794 --> 16:34.428
My fault.

16:34.461 --> 16:37.197
Your hurt your father!

16:37.231 --> 16:40.635
After he bring
all those noodles for you.

16:40.668 --> 16:43.270
I set timer now.

16:43.303 --> 16:45.138
Ten minutes.

16:45.172 --> 16:48.408
- No more.
- That's right.

16:48.442 --> 16:51.378
You want a sticker, you have
to put those noodles away

16:51.411 --> 16:53.213
