18:40.722 --> 18:41.889
No, no, no.

18:41.923 --> 18:44.626
Not if you're staying here.

18:44.659 --> 18:47.829
But your mother and I think
you should consider moving,

18:47.862 --> 18:49.396
not renovating.

18:49.429 --> 18:51.465
There are some nice places near
the canal.

18:51.498 --> 18:53.367
We checked.

18:53.400 --> 18:55.268
We're not moving.

18:55.302 --> 18:56.571
Sweetheart?

18:56.604 --> 19:01.843
Why beat a dead horse?

19:01.876 --> 19:05.178
So, when does she plan on
making the big ask?

19:05.212 --> 19:07.649
After dessert?

19:07.682 --> 19:09.584
Oh, the...

19:09.617 --> 19:11.886
God, don't play innocent
with me, Charles.

19:11.919 --> 19:15.823
I'll be surprised if she hasn't
catered the entire meal.

19:15.857 --> 19:20.193
Hired a Master of Ceremonies.

19:20.227 --> 19:21.639
Wish someone would tell her
she doesn't have to treat us

19:21.663 --> 19:27.802
like we're potential
corporate sponsors.

19:27.835 --> 19:30.738
I haven't been entirely
truthful.

19:30.772 --> 19:33.574
It is a fact that
I've never seen one of Cody's

19:33.608 --> 19:37.244
full-blown fits,
but I've sensed something.

19:37.277 --> 19:38.646
Nothing I could put a finger on.

19:38.680 --> 19:42.349
Just a feeling that things
weren't quite right.

19:42.382 --> 19:45.452
I love my daughter dearly.

19:45.485 --> 19:49.724
But she has a tendency
to let hope outlast the truth.

19:53.027 --> 19:55.495
