26:31.826 --> 26:33.928
Marry me.

26:33.961 --> 26:36.931
Come back to Seattle
and marry me.

26:36.964 --> 26:42.269
Today, tomorrow,
in a year, soon.

26:42.303 --> 26:44.839
Yes! Yes!

26:48.976 --> 26:51.245
I have a surprise
for the two of you.

26:51.278 --> 26:53.380
Oh yeah?

26:53.414 --> 26:55.683
Your father and I are taking
Cody for the next four days,

26:55.716 --> 26:59.420
so the two of you
can get away together.

26:59.453 --> 27:02.756
I know his routine and rules.

27:02.790 --> 27:06.327
He can't be touched on the neck,
especially when eating.

27:06.360 --> 27:08.729
No, Mother. No, no, no.

27:08.762 --> 27:11.298
We can't... we can't
possibly get away

27:11.332 --> 27:12.967
with everything with going on.

27:13.000 --> 27:15.078
- I'm sorry, this is not...
